## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all recent developments in legal technology. The findings are limited to the sources reviewed, and there may be other significant advancements not covered in this report. Additionally, the impact of technology on smaller law firms versus larger firms may vary, and this report does not differentiate between these experiences.